      <title>尽管特朗普威胁征收关税，台湾仍上调 2025 年 GDP 预测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/taiwan-lifts-2025-gdp-forecast-despite-trump-s-tariff-threats</link>
