    <item>
      <title>土耳其经济在利率决定前陷入衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/turkey-s-economy-posts-limited-growth-amid-high-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其第三季度因工业生产暴跌而进入技术性衰退，这为央行考虑是否在下个月开始降息提供了更多证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/turkey-s-economy-posts-limited-growth-amid-high-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 07:03:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼股市因经济增长放缓进入调整期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/indonesian-stocks-head-for-correction-on-slowing-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼基准股指较年内高点下跌 10%，进入技术性回调阶段，因唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国大选后经济增长放缓和地区不确定性加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/indonesian-stocks-head-for-correction-on-slowing-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 03:43:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球基金在股票资金外流中发现印度的亮点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/global-funds-find-bright-spots-in-india-despite-equity-outflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管上个月印度股市的资金流出量创下了历史新高，但海外投资者仍在印度寻找投资机会，这表明特定行业仍有潜力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/global-funds-find-bright-spots-in-india-despite-equity-outflows</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
